gue Cup, Scottish Cup and Uefa Cup. '''Total''': Total No. of competitive goals scored.</small>\n\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Discipline===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n!align=left|Name\n!{{Fb red card}}\n!{{Fb second yellow card}}\n!{{Fb yellow card}}\n!Total\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Lee Miller (footballer)|Lee Miller]] || || 1|| 9|| '''11'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Zander Diamond]] || || || 7|| '''7'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Richard Foster (footballer)|Richard Foster]] || || || 6|| '''6'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Derek Young]] || || || 6|| '''6'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Andrew Considine]] || || || 5|| '''5'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Darren Mackie]] || || || 5|| '''5'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Barry Nicholson]] || || || 5|| '''5'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Scott Severin]] || || || 5|| '''5'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|NED}} [[Karim Touzani]] || || || 4|| '''4'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Josh Walker (English footballer)|Josh Walker]] || || || 4|| '''4'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Michael Hart (footballer)|Michael Hart]] || || || 3|| '''3'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|NED}} [[Jeffrey de Visscher]]  || || || 3|| '''3'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Alan Maybury]] || || || 3|| '''3'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Chris Clark (footballer, born 1980)|Chris Clark]] || || || 2|| '''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Lee Mair]] || || || 2|| '''2'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|NGA}} [[Sone Aluko]] || || || 1|| '''1'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Richie Byrne]] || || || 1|| '''1'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jamie Langfield]] || || || 1|| '''1'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Chris Maguire]] || || || 2|| '''2'''\n|-bgcolor=\"#EFEFEF\"\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jamie Smith (footballer born 1980)|Jamie Smith]] || || || 2|| '''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jackie McNamara]] || || || 1|| '''1'''\n|}\n\n<small>Source: [http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aberdeen/club_stats/default.stm BBC Sport]<br />\nOrdered by: {{Fb red card}}, {{Fb second yellow card}}, {{Fb yellow card}} then Name <br />\n'''Name''': Players's Name, flag next to name indicates player's nationality. {{Fb red card}}: No. of [[Penalty card#Red card|sending offs]] by direct red card. {{Fb second yellow card}}: No. of sending offs by second yellow card. {{Fb yellow card}}: No. of [[Penalty card#Yellow card|bookings]].</small>\n\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Competitions==\n\n===Overall===\n{{fb overall competition header }}\n{{fb overall2 competition|bg=|cl=[[2007\u201308 Scottish Premier League|Scottish Premier League]]|srn=\u2014|fp=4|fprn=4|dm=|dfm=4 August 2007|dlm=22 May 2008 }}\n{{fb overall2 competition|bg=y|cl=[[2007\u201308 UEFA Cup|UEFA Cup]]|srn=[[2007\u201308 UEFA Cup#First round|First Round]]|fp=|fprn=[[2007\u201308 UEFA Cup#Round of 32|Round of 32]]|dm=|dfm=20 September 2007|dlm=22 February 2008 }}\n{{fb overall2 competition|bg=|cl=[[2007\u201308 Scottish League Cup|Scottish League Cup]]|srn=[[2007\u201308 Scottish League Cup#Third Round|Third Round]]|fp=|fprn=[[2007\u201308 Scottish League Cup#Semi Finals|Semi Finals]]|dm=|dfm=26 September 2007|dlm=5 February 2008 }}\n{{fb overall2 competition|bg=y|cl=[[2007\u201308 Scottish Cup|Scottish Cup]]|srn=[[2007\u201308 Scottish Cup#Fourth round|Fourth round]]|fp=|fprn=[[2007\u201308 Scottish Cup#Semi Finals|Semi Finals]]|dm=|dfm=12 January 2008|dlm=12 April 2008 }}\n{{fb overall competition footer}}\n\n===SPL===\n{{main|2007\u201308 Scottish Premier League}}\n====Classification====\n{{:2007\u201308 Scottish Premier League|showteam=ABE}}\n\n====Results summary====\n{{Fb_rs |hw=11 |hd=5 |hl=4 |hgf=33 |hga=21 |aw=4 |ad=3 |al=11 |agf=17 |aga=37 }}\n\n{{Fb_rs_footer |s=[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aberdeen/tables/default.stm BBC Sport] |date=December 2012}}\n\n====Results by round====\n{{#invoke:sports rbr table|table|legendpos=b\n|header=Round\n|label1= Ground\n|res1=A /H /H /A /A /H /A /H /H /A /H /H /A /A /H /H /A /H /A /A /H /A /A /H /H /A /A /H /A /H /H /A /H /A /H /H /A /H\n|label2= Result\n|res2=L /D /L /D /W /L /L /W /W /W /D /W /L /L /W /W /L /D /D /W /W /D /L /L /L /L /L /D /L /W /D /W /W /L /W /W /L /W\n<!-- -->\n|text_H=Home|text_A=Away\n|color_W=green2|text_W=Win\n|color_D=yellow2|text_D=Draw\n|color_L=red2|text_L=Loss\n\n|source=[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aberdeen/results/default.stm BBC Sport]\n|date=December 2012\n}}\n\n==Club==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===The management===\n{{Fb cs header}}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=  |p=Manager           |s={{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jimmy Calderwood]] }}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=y |p=Assistant manager |s={{flagicon|NIR}} [[Jimmy Nicholl]] }}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=  |p=Striker coach     |s={{flagicon|SCO}} [[Sandy Clark]] }}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=y |p=Goalkeeping coach |s={{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jim Leighton]] }}\n{{Fb cs footer|date=February 2008}}\n\n===Other information===\n{{fb oi header}}\n{{Fb oi information |bg=  |id=Chairman           |i={{flagicon|SCO}} [[Stewart Milne]] }}\n{{Fb oi information |bg=y |id=Managing Director  |i={{flagicon|SCO}} Duncan Fraser }}\n{{Fb oi information |bg=  |id=Executive Director |i={{flagicon|SCO}} [[Willie Miller]] }}\n{{fb oi information |bg=y |id={{Fb oi ground}}   |i={{Fb oi ground |g=[[Pittodrie Stadium]] |c=22,199 |d=109x72 yards}} }}\n{{fb oi footer |s=[http://www.afc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/Home afc.co.uk]|date=December 2012}}\n\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Team kit===\n{{Fb_kit_header |su=[[Nike, Inc.|Nike]] |sp=Apex Tubulars/[[Acergy]]}}\n|{{Football kit\n|pattern_la = _whiteborder\n|pattern_b  = _whitecollar\n|pattern_ra = _whiteborder\n|leftarm    = FF0000\n|body       = FF0000\n|rightarm   = FF0000\n|shorts     = FF0000\n|socks      = FF0000\n|title      = Home}}\n|{{Football kit\